## AI-Assisted Predictive Maintenance System for Rotating Machinery

**Status:** In Development

Unexpected equipment failures remain one of the biggest challenges in industrial operations. This project explores Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning techniques to predict failures in rotating machinery using vibration, temperature, and operational data.

### Technologies

- Python
- Machine Learning
- Predictive Maintenance
- Data Analysis
- Vibration Monitoring

### Knowledge Areas

- Reliability Engineering
- Rotating Machinery
- Condition Monitoring
- Industrial AI

